Package: org.codehaus.groovy.grails.resolve.maven.aether.support

[Groovy] Class MultipleTopLevelJavaScopeSelector

      • org.codehaus.groovy.grails.resolve.maven.aether.support.MultipleTopLevelJavaScopeSelector

      • The default org.eclipse.aether.util.graph.transformer.JavaScopeSelector just takes whatever is the first top-level dependency as the valid scope without comparing the effective scope of multiple. This class fixes that
